# .env.example — structure reference only.
#
# The live key file is .env (gitignored).
# .env contains the full key structure with real values where set
# and empty placeholders where not.
#
# To set up on a fresh clone:
#   cp .env .env.backup    # optional — save your keys before resetting
#   # Then fill in the keys you have. The full structure is in .env.
#
# v1.0.0 required keys:
#   ANTHROPIC_API_KEY    — claude-sonnet-4-5
#   GROQ_API_KEY         — llama-3.3-70b-versatile (free tier)
#   GOOGLE_API_KEY       — gemini-3.5-flash (free tier)
#
# Ollama needs no key — just run: ollama serve && ollama pull llama3.1:8b
